updates.title: VAICOM PRO Community Edition for DCS World
updates.releasenotes: Couple more bug fixes due to typos, Additional Afghan Chatter files, Adds F-5E Flaming Cliffs version, Adds community Super Hornet mod F/A-18E/F and EA-18G, Adds Chatter theme Afghan (WIP) at this stage only has about half the intended sound files.
